{"name": "Checks - for a Cause 1", "description": "Hello everyone. This is a mint for charity using the Checks framework.
My family has been devastated by the onset of Alzheimer's Disease and Dementia, losing my grandmother to the disease in 2022.

I am hoping to use the social media attention of Jack Butcher and his innovative project to do some good. 

100% of the proceeds from this mint will be donated to the Fisher Center for  Alzheimer's Research Foundation (https://www.alzinfo.org/) 

I'm a fan of Jack's work because he skillfully conveys meaningful stories through culturally significant imagery. I appreciate the themes of his work with his company, Visualize Value, such as self-improvement and the effort required to create great products, which resonates with me.
